


Abstraction
             Abstraction provides generalization.   General objects of type HOUR TIMESHEET while the objects are of type Weekly and biWeekly timesheet.
             Hides functionality;
             Partial Abstraction/Complete Abstraction
             Abstract class/Interface



Encapsulation:-
               Hides unwanted implementation details from users of an object;
               Hides data;
               private variable of calss -> can access them with only getters and setters.

               Improve re-usability.
               Make our code more maintainable
               loosely coupled code makes testing easier.




